ough. He displays the utmost professionalism. He made sure all of our questions were answered before we left. Dr. McAdams valued our input and gave us honest feedback on issues we were concerned about. You can tell he is passionate about dentistry and patient care. He even gave us a little info regarding the architecture of the office. This just proves that there is thought behind every detail in the office.

